  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Initial Central Mexico Earthquake Response</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This is in response to the earthquake disaster in southern Mexico. We will be focusing on food security and shelter to 1,500 households. We will be focusing on the municipalities of Juchitan and Ixtaltepec in Oaxaca and Tonala, Arriaga and Cintalapa in Chiapa</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We will be distributing food baskets to 1,500 households which will provide food for seven days. We will also be providing sheets for roofing to 714 families which will be selected after evaluation.</narrative>
  </description>
